name: Ej Tumaneng
text: Q1 for me is tough to answer, i guess i'll say 'none'. I only have one bet. if he decides not to run, i'll abstain. i guess the candidates themselves would have the same answer. except duterte who already said he'll support/vote binay if he gets DQed.
